There will be much wine, the sciences - they will unite again, and so will the crafts, there will be many lamps burning whale oil, and there will be no plastic to be found. New arts will be made, foreign for our eyes still. Land will flow, and new continents will await us. Yes!
No good labour of ours will be forgotten in the coming age. A Flood comes to wash away the world, but all of good quality and purity is saved in the Arc.

The Arc symbolizes not just an annihilation, but a cleanse. What is ugly, evil, twisted, gets washed away, what has remained good and even developed continues forwards into the next world. This is why it's still important to act well, to build, create, etc.
